// Look into the interview with the person with the same id
SELECT *
FROM interview 
WHERE person_id = 67318

--------- Findings ---------
1. I was hired by a woman with a lot of money. I don't know her name but I know she's around 5'5" (65") 
or 5'7" (67"). She has red hair and she drives a Tesla Model S. I know that she attended the 
SQL Symphony Concert 3 times in December 2017.







