In conclusion, Jeremy Bowers was hired by Miranda Priestly at the SQL Symphony that occured on December 6 2017
to commit a murder which took place a month later on January 15 2018. He was paid considerably according to his
confession/interview. Miranda makes around 310,000 while Bowers makes only around 10,500. 

